  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "YoYo's Puzzle Park (released as \"Gussun Paradise\" in Japan) is a puzzle platform game featuring some sixty platform-filled levels similar to Bubble Bobble. The player (as Guss or Yodie) can hop around on them, while avoiding the enemies that crowd the platforms. ... In the multi-player mode, you can fight against your friends in a two-player deathmatch game.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
